# masterplan.md

## Project Title
Personal Profile Website on GitHub Pages

## Objective
Create a responsive, visually clean, and easily customizable personal profile website hosted on GitHub Pages (username.github.io). The site will include personal information, contact details, links to work or projects, and optionally a resume or blog.

---

## Features

### 1. Home Page
- Personal introduction (name, tagline)
- Profile picture
- Responsive hero section
- Call-to-action (e.g., download resume or contact me)

### 2. About Section
- Short bio
- Skills summary
- Work or academic background (simple timeline or list)

### 3. Projects or Portfolio
- List of selected projects with:
  - Title
  - Short description
  - GitHub repo or live link
  - Optional thumbnail or image

### 4. Contact Section
- Email link
- Social media links (GitHub, LinkedIn, etc.)
- Optional contact form (emailJS or Formspree)

### 5. Resume (Optional)
- Button to download a PDF resume
- Or embedded resume section

---

## Pages
- `index.html` (main profile + sections)
- Optional: `blog.html` or `resume.html`

---

## Styling & Design
- Clean and minimal design (Tailwind CSS or plain CSS)
- Light/dark mode toggle (optional)
- Mobile responsive (Flexbox/Grid)

---

## Hosting Instructions
- Hosted on GitHub Pages
- Automatically builds from `main` or `gh-pages` branch
- Uses custom domain support (optional)

---

